Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:22.12,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru (get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:24.50,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:29.88,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,錆びついた　shadow prison　姿潜めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:34.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,行き場を探しては　I keep my soul in you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.43,0:02:36.97,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,So break out so break out -> To battle the tension
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.97,0:02:39.22,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Never give up that fight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:41.77,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,So break out so break out -> To battle the tension
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:44.44,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Don't let it claim your light rise
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:49.27,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,果てなきを彷徨う　飽く無き声が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:54.15,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,足枷を解いて　羽ばたくの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:56.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,時間の狭間で召されてく魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:02:59.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,たとえ全てを焼き尽くされたとし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:04.08,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,ても　飲み込んで　しまえば
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:08.96,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,闇を振り翳して　胸に宿すアンサー
